User and Server

1. user --> server
    login/logoff
    status
2. server --> user
    online/offline
3. user --> user
    direct message
    boardcast message
    

Commands:

    login <username> <password>
    reg <username> <password>
    logoff
    msg <user> text.....
    broadcast text.....
    multicast <n> user1 user2 ... text...
    req <user>
    ac <user>

    show 
    multicast 3 a b c msg
    guest : "msg jim Hello world"
    naimul: "msg guest Hello world"

    @group <-- group chat
    join @group
    leave @group
    

    send: msg @group text...
    recieve: msg @group:<login> text.... 
    
   